<script type="text/babel">
import Vue from "vue";
export default Vue.component("vue-frame", {
  props: {
    url: {
      type: String,
      required: true
    },
    text: {
      type: String,
      required: true
    },
    frame: {
      type: String,
      required: true
    },
    type: {
      type: String,
      required: false,
      default: "a"
    },
    default: {
      type: Boolean,
      required: false,
      default: false
    }
  },
  data: function() {
    return {};
  },
  mounted: function() {
    if (this.default == true) {
      this.loadIframe()
    }
  },
  methods: {
    loadIframe: function() {
      // console.log("Iframe:", this.url, this.frame, this.type);
      var iframe = document.getElementById(this.frame);
      iframe.src = this.url;
      iframe.onload = function() {
        // console.log("iframe cargado...")
      };
    }
  },
  render: function(createElement) {
    return createElement(
      this.type, // tag name
      {
        // DOM properties
        domProps: {
          innerHTML: this.text
        },
        on: {
          click: this.loadIframe
        }
      }
    );
  }
});

// create a root instance
new Vue({
  name: "vue-frame",
  el: "#app"
});
</script>
